---
import SiteLayout from "../components/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="三维高斯泼溅场景渲染"
  description="展示基于车端标定相机、位姿数据、点云初始化和 A100 训练的 3DGS 场景渲染链路。"
  currentPath="/three-dgs"
>
  <header class="page-hero three-dgs-hero">
    <img
      src="/assets/hero-cloud-ops.png"
      alt="三维高斯泼溅场景渲染"
      class="hero-media"
      data-parallax
    />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-grid"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-shell">
      <div class="page-hero-copy reveal" data-reveal>
        <p class="page-kicker">PAGE 09 · 3D GAUSSIAN SPLATTING</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">三维高斯泼溅场景渲染</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">
          通过车端标定相机和 /ndt_pose 采集图像-位姿关键帧，结合 GlobalMap.pcd 初始化高斯点，并在云端完成规整、训练和查看。公开页面展示链路；采集、上传和训练进入私有工作台后按权限开放。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page-main grid-bg">
    <section class="page-section">
      <div class="glass-card section-card reveal" data-reveal>
        <p class="section-kicker">3DGS 链路</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">从车端采集到云端训练查看</h2>
        <div class="page-grid-three">
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>车端采集</h3>
            <p>使用具备正式外参的相机通道采集图像，并同步 /ndt_pose 位姿关键帧。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>数据规整</h3>
            <p>将图像、位姿和点云初始化数据规整为训练所需的数据集结构。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="page-card">
            <h3>云端训练</h3>
            <p>在 A100 上执行 3DGS 训练，并通过 viewer 查看结果、评估质量和调整相机。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="chip-list">
          <a class="chip-item" href="/app/three-dgs">进入 3DGS 工作台</a>
          <span class="chip-item">需要 3DGS 权限</span>
          <span class="chip-item">服务端先鉴权</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
